headline: Costco Expands Levels Whey Protein As Valuation And Membership Story Evolves
summary: Costco Wholesale expanded distribution of Levels Whey Protein across its warehouses in the Pacific Northwest and several additional states. The rollout brings a wider range of high quality, clean label protein products into Costco’s health and wellness assortment. The move supports Costco’s efforts to offer rigorously certified products that cater to growing demand for ingredient transparency and product safety.
